label.pecs:noIFXText: Your computer does not have a required file installed (Toolbar IFX). This will prevent you from saving the form back to the server. Please contact your help desk.
label.pecs:noConnectionText: Portal connectivity is not currently available. Select OK to save the form locally. Select CANCEL if you wish to retry later.
label.pecs:wrongIFXText: This form requires a different version of IFX installed (Toolbar IFX). This will prevent you from saving the form back to the server. Please contact your help desk.

custom:force_offline_mode.xfdl:compute:
// Before Email button fires
toggle(custom:force_offline_event, 'off', 'on') == '1'
// Save url and state information then clear the url and set Open State off
? set('custom:force_offline_event', 'off')
+. set('custom:temp_url', custom:url)
+. set('custom:temp_open_flag', custom:open_flag)
+. set('custom:url', '')
+. set('custom:open_flag', '0')
: ''

custom:restore_online_mode.xfdl:compute:
// After Email button fires
toggle(custom:restore_online_event, 'off', 'on') == '1'
// Restore url and state information then clear temp variables
? set('custom:restore_online_event', 'off')
+. set('custom:url', custom:temp_url)
+. set('custom:open_flag', custom:temp_open_flag)
+. set('custom:temp_url', '')
+. set('custom:temp_open_flag', '')
: ''

custom:before_save.xfdl:compute:
toggle(custom:save_event, 'off', 'on') == '1'
? set('custom:save_event', 'off')
// Submit the form
+. set(custom:triggeritem_page +. '.SUBMIT_ACTION.activated', 'on')
: ''

custom:handle_closeout.xfdl:compute:
// Handle the Open Form RULES on form load
(toggle(global.global.activated, 'off', 'on') == '1' and global.global.printing != 'on'
and set('custom:pre_url', custom:url) == '1'
and set('custom:pre_open_flag', custom:open_flag) == '1')
// EXCEPTION 1: If URL exists and Open Flag is on, then user closed out of the browser
? (custom:url != '' and custom:open_flag == '1')
// Force Off-line mode. Clear URL, set OPEN_FLAG to 1
? set('custom:url', '')
+. set('custom:open_flag', '1')
+. set('custom:temp_url', '')
+. set('custom:temp_open_flag', '')
// Else: Set open flag
: set('custom:open_flag', '1')
+. set('custom:temp_url', '')
+. set('custom:temp_open_flag', '')
: ''

custom:check_ifx.xfdl:compute:
toggle(global.global.activated, 'off', 'on') == '1' and global.global.printing != 'on'
// If IFX is version is not correct
? set('custom:army_package_exists', army_package.ifxExists())
+. (custom:army_package_exists != custom:army_package_version
// If IFX does not exist
? (custom:army_package_exists == ''
? (custom:url != '' ? viewer.messageBox(pecs:noIFXText, 'Warning', OK) : '')
+. set('custom:force_offline_event', 'on')
// Else IFX exist, but is the wrong version
: (custom:url != '' ? viewer.messageBox(pecs:wrongIFXText, 'Warning', OK) : ''))
+. set('custom:force_offline_event', 'on')
// Else IFX is version is correct
: '')
: ''
